To cite package ‘massiR’ in publications use:

Sam Buckberry, Stephen J Bent, Tina Bianco-Miotto and  Claire T Roberts (2014).
massiR: a method for predicting the sex of samples in gene expression microarray datasets 
Bioinformatics, doi: 10.1093/bioinformatics/btu161


A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

@article{
         author = {Buckberry, Sam and Bent, Stephen J and Bianco-Miotto, Tina and Roberts, Claire T}, 
         title = {massiR: a method for predicting the sex of samples in gene expression microarray datasets},
         year = {2014}, 
         doi = {10.1093/bioinformatics/btu161}, 
         URL = {http://bioinformatics.oxfordjournals.org/content/early/2014/03/22/bioinformatics.btu161}, 
         journal = {Bioinformatics} 
}
